version_description:
- Renamed application from F5 Access 2018 to F5 Access.
- Agreement prompt for privacy terms.
- Import directly using a URL link or with a share extension.
- Deploy with a VPN configuration by an MDM service or mobile configuration profile.

- Fixed stability issues with F5Access VPN tunnel. VPN tunnel may crash which will cause session leak and unstable VPN connectivity. it happens mostly with per-app VPN when on demand timeout happens.
- Fix domain cookie, VPN can not be connected in web

- Performance improvement with DTLS channel.
- Fixed removal of cache password due to connectivity change and device reboot
- Show certificates from Settings->Manage Certificates
- Improved usability of DNS errors notification with on-demand v
Bug fixes, and connection stability improvements
